WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.000
Welcome to the advanced video player demo.

00:00:05.000 --> 00:00:10.000
This player supports HLS adaptive streaming.

00:00:10.000 --> 00:00:15.000
You can control playback with keyboard shortcuts.

00:00:15.000 --> 00:00:20.000
Press Space or K to play and pause.

00:00:20.000 --> 00:00:25.000
Use arrow keys to seek and adjust volume.

00:00:25.000 --> 00:00:30.000
Press F for fullscreen mode.

00:00:30.000 --> 00:00:35.000
On mobile, use gestures to control playback.

00:00:35.000 --> 00:00:40.000
Double tap to play or pause.

00:00:40.000 --> 00:00:45.000
Swipe horizontally to seek through the video.

00:00:45.000 --> 00:00:50.000
Swipe vertically on the right to adjust volume.

00:00:50.000 --> 00:00:55.000
Your watch progress is automatically saved.

00:00:55.000 --> 00:01:00.000
Enjoy watching!
